DESIGN:

The parameters are retrieved from request.GET and set to local variables. The value of user_input is checked.
If it is blank, the list of countries is retrieved from database and response is sent. If a country exists
with the given user_input, its capital is retrieved from database and returned. If there is no country with
corresponding user_input, needed error msg is returned.




DEPENDENCY:
django-1.3



USAGE:

Stop apache2 service if it is running 
$sudo service apache2 stop

$sudo python manage.py runserver 0.0.0.0:80
to run the development server in localhost

To add more country and capital list, got to http://localhost/admin
username : codejam
password : c0d3jam!
 

